oblems that require involvement of others to solve. o Has the ability to reach sound decisions quickly. o Carefully evaluates alternative risks and solutions before taking action. o Optimizes the use of all available resources. o Has a solid working knowledge of capabilities and direction of technology, coupled with an in-depth knowledge of the technology required and the needs of business environment necessary to support business roadmaps. o Develops solutions to meet business needs that reflect a clear understanding of the objectives, practices and procedures of the corporation, department and business unit. Team Orientation: Maintains partnerships across the organization, and is able to influence senior management, peers and staff through an inclusive style and recognition of their abilities to achieve results. Self-Management: Responsibilities are assigned with latitude for setting priorities and decision-making using accepted guidelines. Results are reviewed with next level manager for clarification according to predefined objectives Commitment to Quality Result: Creates an atmosphere where business partner's issues are dealt with professionally, and in a timely manner. Suggests solutions that make sense and are in line with future technology direction. Communicates openly and effectively in a manner consistent with the audience. Demonstrates an adaptive style that is flexible and effective in gaining cooperation of others. Anticipates and responds to management requests for information with timely, accurate findings. Planning and Project Management: Proposes plans of action that are timely, realistic and positive. Sets appropriate goals for initiatives, and monitors progress. Equal Employment Opportunity Statement Travelers is an equal opportunity employer. ", 
